{"tid":221066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【曱甴復仇記】噴酒精點火 日男疑燒曱甴引發奪命火","createTime":"2017-04-28T12:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T20:00:44.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8b5a0f61e23829aeba61de6e80ee89686e3972","tid":221066,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>【曱甴復仇記】噴酒精點火 日男疑燒曱甴引發奪命火</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時國際 <br />\n<br />\n2017-04-28 16:44:41 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本廣島縣廣島市一棟建築物前年10月發生大火，造成3死3傷。警方經調查後，懷疑一名男子驅趕曱甴時意外引起火災。<br />\n<br />\n起火建築物位於廣島市的繁華街，建築物內設有女僕咖啡店等店舖。當局相信地下的垃圾收集處是起火源頭，而當時一名20多歲的餐廳男職員為了驅趕曱甴，在垃圾收集處附近向曱甴噴灑酒精噴霧，其後用火槍點火燒曱甴。<br />\n<br />\n警方推斷，火勢隨曱甴走進垃圾堆後，蔓延到整棟建築物。當局正作進一步調查，或以嚴重過失失火、嚴重過失致死傷的罪名控告涉案男子。"},{"pid":"d502420fc235b68ffb00a8c0d0e51c4a050f1c09","tid":221066,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"當隻強哥異形咁殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a10ef27c9b6e83d18457e996402c019fb5d9e84","tid":221066,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"間野防火應該有問題"},{"pid":"625d752b02b2a54286ce16d6838e1bf933a66fa6","tid":221066,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"屌 我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n立刻用花灑求火"},{"pid":"eb2ff887d8a5807ba7006e4ea2361847cd21f952","tid":221066,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:38:44.000Z","msg":"係咪傻㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0aa72bd58385d7733bafad753e63d8cb194509","tid":221066,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:45:23.000Z","msg":"小強死左未"},{"pid":"119714adf883a726091a426d6b1e5e160504d287","tid":221066,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:48:00.000Z","msg":"要死都要你班人類一齊<img 